import requests
import re
 
websites = ['http://example.com', 'http://google.com', 'http://sample.com']
 
#Regex setfor scan
sqlRegex = '(\%3D)|(\")|(--)|(\/\*)'      #usedannotation
xssRegex = '[\w!\\'$\\”$^]*\\<script\\>'
 
for site in websites:
    value = requests.get(site).content
    foundSQLInjection = False
    foundXSS = False
    if re.compile(sqlRegex).findall(value.decode('utf-8')) != []:
        foundSQLInjection = True
    if re.compile(xssRegex).findall(value):
      foundXSS = True
    
    print(('The website {}-{}. No SQL Injection found-{}, XSS found-{}'
            .format(site, value.decode('utf-8') ,foundSQLInjection, foundXSS)))
